Come here! I want you to see this!

30
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:35,670
Didn't you say that you like him?

31
00:03:35,670 --> 00:03:38,480
I want you to see him die!

32
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,490
No!

33
00:03:51,370 --> 00:03:54,070
Open your eyes and look!

34
00:03:54,070 --> 00:03:56,440
Look at it!

35
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,310
Release the arrows!

36
00:04:30,230 --> 00:04:31,850
No.

37
00:04:41,460 --> 00:04:43,010
No...

38
00:05:04,610 --> 00:05:06,460
Release the arrows.

39
00:05:11,790 --> 00:05:14,900
Li Chengyin, stop right now! Stop right now!

40
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:18,460
You cannot keep shooting. You cannot keep shooting!

41
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:21,130
Aside from Gu Jian, A'Du is there, too.

42
00:05:21,130 --> 00:05:24,930
What did A'Du do wrong?! What did A'Du do wrong?!

43
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:27,130
Hurry and stop!

44
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:37,440
Hurry and stop! Hurry and stop!

45
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:42,360
Li Chengyin, I beg you. Please stop!

46
00:05:45,050 --> 00:05:47,440
Hurry!

47
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,820
Stop!

48
00:06:41,230 --> 00:06:43,820
Gu Jian!

49
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,690
Gu Jian!

50
00:07:03,690 --> 00:07:06,870
Gu Jian! Gu Jian!

51
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:11,180
A'Du...

52
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:15,480
A'Du is all right.

53
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:18,660
You saved her. She is alive.

54
00:07:35,450 --> 00:07:37,390
A'Du...

55
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:41,750
If something happens to her,

56
00:07:42,910 --> 00:07:46,820
you will be devastated.

57
00:07:50,250 --> 00:07:51,890
I...

58
00:07:51,890 --> 00:07:58,000
I cannot let you be sad anymore.

59
00:08:00,450 --> 00:08:03,120
You hid her under you.

60
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:06,580
You were protecting her, right?

61
00:08:06,580 --> 00:08:08,670
Right?

62
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:25,100
Why are you so foolish?

63
00:08:27,760 --> 00:08:30,420
Why are you so foolish?

64
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:33,460
I did you wrong.

