81
00:10:32,090 --> 00:10:39,270
♫ What's wrong with fake happiness, since no one is
there to share it with ♫

82
00:10:40,070 --> 00:10:46,840
♫ You were once my frontier ♫

83
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:50,630
♫ Resisting all my sorrows ♫

84
00:10:50,630 --> 00:10:53,510
I just want to be with the person I love

85
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:56,860
and live a careless and free life.

86
00:10:58,130 --> 00:10:59,770
Xiaofeng,

87
00:10:59,770 --> 00:11:04,360
if you weren't the ninth princess of Xi State, I would take you with me.

88
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:12,720
♫ Lightly removing my clothes, swallowing my tears
to put on a joyful makeup ♫

89
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:19,360
♫ Waiting for you to put on your armor, and howl at the vicissitudes of life ♫

90
00:11:19,360 --> 00:11:23,630
♫ The past eventually can't stop its own flow ♫

91
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:29,280
♫ Go ride your sword and fly, and you might be able to fly away ♫

92
00:11:29,280 --> 00:11:32,420
What you said about thinking for my sake, doing it for my good, were all lies.

93
00:11:32,420 --> 00:11:34,330
You liar!

94
00:11:34,330 --> 00:11:37,520
Xiaofeng, you shouldn't stay here.

95
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:41,380
You shouldn't sacrifice your happiness and marry someone you don't love.

96
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:53,200
♫ The boat passes an empty harbor and feeds the loneliness ♫

97
00:11:53,200 --> 00:11:59,810
♫ Frost falls over the wilderness, drooping the tears ♫

98
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:04,050
♫ Who caused my sun to fall from the sky ♫

99
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:09,290
Xiaofeng, who I am isn't important.

100
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:11,710
What's important is that I will take you back to Xi State.

101
00:12:11,710 --> 00:12:13,530
I will take you home.

102
00:12:13,530 --> 00:12:20,220
♫ Setting sail to a far land, but couldn't get over being perplexed ♫

103
00:12:20,220 --> 00:12:26,950
♫ In coping while in exile, you can't fight against desolation ♫

104
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:31,120
♫ I want to dive into the sea of memories ♫

105
00:12:31,120 --> 00:12:41,320
♫ To search for your image, for only you are my heaven ♫

106
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:44,610
♫ For only you are ... my heaven ♫

107
00:12:44,610 --> 00:12:46,410
Gu Jian.

108
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:49,430
Gu Jian. Gu Jian!

109
00:12:55,010 --> 00:12:57,280
Wake up!

110
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:02,500
Teacher! Teacher, wake up!

111
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:04,500
I'll go back to Xi State with you.

112
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:06,730
Hurry and wake up.

113
00:13:06,730 --> 00:13:08,980
Quickly wake up...

114
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:13,360
Hurry and wake up!

115
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:16,170
Wake up! We'll leave now! I'll leave with you!

116
00:13:16,170 --> 00:13:18,770
Let's go back to Xi State!

117
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:21,170
Can someone save him?

118
00:13:21,970 --> 00:13:25,120
Can someone save him?!

119
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:28,590
I'll go back with you to Xi State.

120
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:30,920
I'll go back with you.

121
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,850
Can you hear me?

122
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:53,370
Teacher!

123
00:13:56,270 --> 00:14:01,010
The date we promised is the fifteenth of the seventh month when it's a full moon.

124
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:04,800
We promised that you would wait for me on the sand dunes by the border.

125
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,380
I'd take you to explore the world.

126
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:09,630
You mean we were planning to elope?

127
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:13,150
Then, why didn't you take me away with you?

128
00:14:15,020 --> 00:14:17,090
I did you wrong.

129
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:22,960
Something urgent came up that day, so I couldn't come and find you.

130
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:26,000
By the time I got to the sand dune,

131
00:14:26,650 --> 00:14:28,730
the date we promised to meet already past.

132
00:14:28,730 --> 00:14:36,780
♫ A fox. It's sitting on top of the sand dune ♫

133
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:45,430
♫ Sitting on top of the sand dune, looking at the moon ♫

134
00:14:45,430 --> 00:14:53,700
♫ But actually, it's not watching the moon ♫

135
00:14:53,700 --> 00:15:01,710
♫ It's waiting for the shepherd girl to come back ♫

136
00:15:04,460 --> 00:15:12,760
♪ A fox. It's sitting on top of the sand dune ♪

137
00:15:12,760 --> 00:15:20,010
♪ Sitting on top of the sand dune, basking under the sun ♪

138
00:15:20,010 --> 00:15:26,770
♪ But actually, it's not basking under the sun ♪

139
00:15:28,590 --> 00:15:35,910
♪ It's waiting for the girl riding a horse to pass by ♪

140
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:42,750
♪ But looking at the moon, ♪

141
00:15:43,470 --> 00:15:48,370
♪ the fox only saw desolate ♪

142
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:13,960
Crown Princess Consort. Crown Princess Consort.

143
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,610
Go away!

144
00:16:15,610 --> 00:16:19,620
♫ The fox... ♫

145
00:16:19,620 --> 00:16:24,030
♫ The fox... ♫

146
00:16:24,030 --> 00:16:32,400
♫ could not wait for the shepherd girl to come back ♫

147
00:16:32,400 --> 00:16:37,220
♫ The fox... ♫

148
00:16:37,220 --> 00:16:40,320
He's dead.

149
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:48,090
Are you that devastated?

150
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:53,110
♫ The fox is thinking ♫

151
00:16:53,110 --> 00:16:54,820
Yes.

152
00:16:55,890 --> 00:17:00,590
♫ A fox ♫

153
00:17:00,590 --> 00:17:04,490
I'm very devastated.

154
00:17:06,330 --> 00:17:08,690
Are you satisfied now?

155
00:17:11,760 --> 00:17:14,350
Are you satisfied now?

156
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:24,380
You love him that much?

157
00:17:25,360 --> 00:17:27,940
You really want to kill me now?

158
00:17:38,630 --> 00:17:41,760
My Gu Xiaowu has died.

159
00:17:45,430 --> 00:17:47,730
He is forever dead.

160
00:17:54,190 --> 00:17:57,550
You personally killed him.

161
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,910
Then hate me.

162
00:18:18,260 --> 00:18:22,920
Hate is better than treating me like nothing.

163
00:18:59,840 --> 00:19:02,960
My Lord, he is the subordinate of the late Yi Moyan.

164
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:05,630
After the battle, Yi Moyan's army was completely annihilated.

165
00:19:05,630 --> 00:19:07,400
He ended up being saved by refugees.

166
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:10,700
He hid in the mountain caves and has been dragging out his feeble existence until now.

167
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:17,270
You have a blessed life.

168
00:19:30,010 --> 00:19:32,680
What's the meaning of you continuing to live?

169
00:19:33,990 --> 00:19:36,250
You want revenge,

170
00:19:36,250 --> 00:19:42,050
or do you want to see your enemies living very well?

171
00:19:43,190 --> 00:19:44,970
You might as well just die.

172
00:19:44,970 --> 00:19:50,310
After you die, you'll be able to see Khan Tömür,

173
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:53,340
the men that have fought along your side, along with

174
00:19:53,340 --> 00:19:57,620
the family members that you have been longing for.

175
00:19:57,620 --> 00:20:03,910
No matter what happens, it will be better than living like how you are now.

176
00:20:05,490 --> 00:20:10,590
I forgot that you don't have the ability to choose between dying or living right now.

177
00:20:14,370 --> 00:20:16,780
If you want to die, it's fine.

178
00:20:19,890 --> 00:20:25,010
If you expose the conspiracy between the Danchi and Gao Xian back then,

179
00:20:25,010 --> 00:20:28,320
I will then give you a quick and satisfying death.

180
00:20:31,260 --> 00:20:33,860
Maybe, you will hate me.

181
00:20:33,860 --> 00:20:38,320
But I wasn't the person who annihilated Danchi.

182
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:41,810
So not only should you not hate me,

183
00:20:41,810 --> 00:20:44,050
you should also thank me.

184
00:20:44,050 --> 00:20:49,220
I, the new ruler of Danchi, used only two years

185
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:52,420
to recover the vegetation and domestication of this place.

186
00:20:52,420 --> 00:20:55,750
All the citizens are living in peace and prosperity.

187
00:20:55,750 --> 00:21:02,690
So, choosing to work with me isn't betrayal.

188
00:21:08,010 --> 00:21:13,730
Father, I've never seen His Imperial Majesty so smitten to a woman.

189
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:16,860
Ever since she entered the palace, whenever His Imperial Majesty comes to the harem,

190
00:21:16,860 --> 00:21:19,680
he will surely stay at that vixen's place.

191
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:24,510
For her, he desolated the other concubines in the harem.

192
00:21:24,510 --> 00:21:26,230
I can not understand it.

193
00:21:26,230 --> 00:21:29,380
She is just a commoner; a lowly servant from a brothel.

194
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:31,300
How could she have smitten His Imperial Majesty like that?

195
00:21:31,300 --> 00:21:36,180
Daughter, after today, do not say such things anymore.

196
00:21:37,390 --> 00:21:38,810
Be patient.

197
00:21:38,810 --> 00:21:41,260
There's no need to fight for affections that will only last for a short moment.

198
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:45,850
Unlike in the past, we are now in a tight position.

199
00:21:45,850 --> 00:21:48,900
It's better to have one less thing to worry about.

200
00:21:51,850 --> 00:21:56,470
I understand, but I'm still angry.

201
00:21:57,090 --> 00:22:01,470
You are a noble consort. You have to be tolerant.

202
00:22:01,470 --> 00:22:05,610
The better you are to Mingyue, the more considerate His Imperial Majesty will be to you.

203
00:22:05,610 --> 00:22:07,240
Am I right?

204
00:22:11,460 --> 00:22:13,370
I know already.

205
00:22:13,370 --> 00:22:16,140
I just wanted to complain.

206
00:22:18,970 --> 00:22:24,800
If you want the emperor to come, go find the grand empress dowager.

207
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:31,390
I understand now.

208
00:22:33,600 --> 00:22:35,440
Thank you, Father.

209
00:22:36,230 --> 00:22:40,070
Send some more smart servants to Mingyue's place.

210
00:22:40,780 --> 00:22:46,120
Father, why are you careful to this extent?

211
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:50,200
One needs to be cautious in order to live longer.

212
00:22:55,380 --> 00:22:57,270
I know now.

213
00:23:01,210 --> 00:23:04,240
Come. Come, come, come.

214
00:23:07,540 --> 00:23:10,750
Leave, leave, leave.

215
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:17,890
North Subduing Marquis, you've drunk the wine and watched the dance.

216
00:23:17,890 --> 00:23:22,330
Just tell me what your motive is for coming here.

217
00:23:23,100 --> 00:23:25,620
King of Shuobo, no need to be nervous.

218
00:23:25,620 --> 00:23:29,590
I am here to give you a present.

219
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:31,570
Stop going in circles.

220
00:23:31,570 --> 00:23:33,890
This little gift of mine

221
00:23:33,890 --> 00:23:39,430
is not as grand as the gift from Lord Gao of the Protectorate General Office of the Western Borders.

222
00:23:42,530 --> 00:23:47,550
Speaking of Lord Gao and the cities that he lost to me,

223
00:23:47,550 --> 00:23:49,880
those indeed count as a magnificent gift.

224
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:53,890
King of Shuobo, you should think about

225
00:23:53,890 --> 00:24:00,900
how things in this world cannot easily have fallen into your hands.

226
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:02,430
What are you trying to say?

227
00:24:02,430 --> 00:24:06,230
The conspiracy between the tribes and the people in charge of guarding the borders.

228
00:24:06,230 --> 00:24:09,420
The frontier pretends as if they are no match,

229
00:24:09,420 --> 00:24:12,780
in exchange for more military power and supplies.

230
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:15,470
The government has no choice but to rely on them heavily

231
00:24:15,470 --> 00:24:18,270
and promote the officials within the borderline.

232
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:22,590
Day after day, year after year, the border is never at peace.

233
00:24:22,590 --> 00:24:26,780
Then the soldiers that guard the border become more important.

234
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:35,320
The idea of raising bandits for one's own benefits is nothing new.

235
00:24:36,540 --> 00:24:41,180
Maybe in the past, Gao Yuming was indeed a big tree that fostered shelter for others.

236
00:24:41,180 --> 00:24:43,650
But now, he is facing enemies from all directions,

237
00:24:43,650 --> 00:24:46,520
His Imperial Majesty's trust for him is less than before.

238
00:24:46,520 --> 00:24:49,710
He is already ordering an investigation.

239
00:24:49,710 --> 00:24:54,210
You, King of Shuobo, are his last move.

240
00:24:54,210 --> 00:24:58,850
He wants to use the clan of Shuobo in his end game.

241
00:24:58,850 --> 00:25:05,190
You wouldn't want to be his stepping stone before he falls, right?

242
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:11,100
I have evidence of the conspiracy between Gao Xian and Danchi.

243
00:25:11,100 --> 00:25:17,090
King of Shuobo, are you interested in taking a look?

244
00:25:17,090 --> 00:25:20,560
Think of how Danchi turned out.

245
00:25:22,200 --> 00:25:25,910
But on the other hand,

246
00:25:25,910 --> 00:25:28,710
if Danchi didn't bring trouble amongst themselves,

247
00:25:28,710 --> 00:25:33,950
I wouldn't be here to give you this big gift.

248
00:25:34,490 --> 00:25:41,900
Next, it all depends whether you, King of Shuobo, would appreciate my kindness.

249
00:26:26,090 --> 00:26:32,380
The way you look when you play the zither reminds me of someone.

250
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:37,560
No wonder, the emperor treasures you.

251
00:26:38,690 --> 00:26:44,790
Also, you have saved his life. It's only natural.

252
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:50,060
However, I know that you are a smart person.

253
00:26:50,060 --> 00:26:54,700
You surely know to do things with propriety.

254
00:26:55,320 --> 00:27:00,840
I understand. I will remember your words, Grand Empress Dowager.

255
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:05,270
Do you usually read books?

256
00:27:05,270 --> 00:27:10,310
I do not read books very often.

257
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:14,200
I only read poems when I have nothing to do.

258
00:27:16,950 --> 00:27:21,020
How about the "Lessons of a Woman," have you read that?

259
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:24,930
You haven't read it.

260
00:27:24,930 --> 00:27:28,680
All right, bring it here.

261
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:38,100
This is a gift from me. Read it.

262
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:42,410
Every day, you will copy it three times.

263
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:49,050
This is both beneficial and helpful to you.

264
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,880
Thank you, Grand Empress Dowager.

265
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:04,930
My Lady.

266
00:28:04,930 --> 00:28:06,070
What's the matter?

267
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:08,980
Grand Empress Dowager went to Mingyue's place and left her a set of the "Lessons of a Woman."

268
00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:11,960
She also told her to copy it three times a day.

269
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,420
Really?

270
00:28:13,420 --> 00:28:14,790
Of course, it's real.

271
00:28:14,790 --> 00:28:16,460
You always have great ideas.

272
00:28:16,460 --> 00:28:21,870
This time that vixen can't live life as easily.

273
00:28:23,870 --> 00:28:26,750
Only making her copy it three times?

274
00:28:26,750 --> 00:28:32,430
The way I see it, three hundred times doesn't even sound like it's too much.

275
00:28:32,430 --> 00:28:34,820
My Lady, just wait.

276
00:28:34,820 --> 00:28:36,980
She is now being watched by Grand Empress Dowager.

277
00:28:36,980 --> 00:28:40,480
We don't have to worry about not having something interesting to watch.

278
00:28:54,960 --> 00:28:57,080
Grand Empress Dowager.

279
00:28:57,080 --> 00:29:00,110
The palace will be quite lively these days.

280
00:29:00,110 --> 00:29:03,750
Earlier, when Xiao Haizi was passing by the Imperial Food Service,

281
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:07,850
he saw Noble Consort Gao heading towards our place from afar.

282
00:29:09,600 --> 00:29:13,260
What else could she be here for?

283
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:15,870
We cannot really blame her for coming here.

284
00:29:15,870 --> 00:29:19,780
I heard that since Miss Mingyue from the brothel entered the palace,

285
00:29:19,780 --> 00:29:23,240
His Imperial Majesty never visited anyone else's place.

286
00:29:23,990 --> 00:29:26,170
Just say that I am resting.

287
00:29:26,170 --> 00:29:28,900
You won't see her, Grand Empress Dowager?

288
00:29:28,900 --> 00:29:30,890
I won't.

289
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:54,320
Everything's my fault.

290
00:29:56,650 --> 00:29:59,870
It's me who killed everyone,

291
00:30:02,140 --> 00:30:05,400
because I fell in love with Gu Xiaowu.

292
00:30:05,950 --> 00:30:08,290
I knew early on that

293
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:12,180
he was not my Gu Xiaowu.

294
00:30:14,360 --> 00:30:17,690
My Gu Xiaowu already died.

295
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:21,270
But why...

296
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:25,500
Why did I remember again?

297
00:30:27,380 --> 00:30:30,980
Is God punishing me?

298
00:30:33,710 --> 00:30:39,660
Punishing me, so I fell in love with the same ruthless person.

299
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:45,380
Punishing me because I killed so many innocent people by my side.

300
00:30:47,010 --> 00:30:53,970
Punishing me to always be lucid and live in pain.

301
00:30:57,670 --> 00:31:00,440
Punishing me...

302
00:31:03,650 --> 00:31:06,130
Punishing me...

303
00:31:19,890 --> 00:31:22,970
Crown Princess Consort, take a sip.

304
00:31:32,480 --> 00:31:34,260
Your Highness the Crown Prince.

305
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:48,830
How many days has she been like this?

306
00:31:49,930 --> 00:31:54,100
Ever since A'Du was brought back here, she has been like this.

307
00:31:59,980 --> 00:32:01,950
Has she eaten food?

308
00:32:03,450 --> 00:32:06,170
She hasn't even drunk a little water.

309
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:41,970
Take a rest.

310
00:32:41,970 --> 00:32:44,900
Even without you, A'Du will not die.

311
00:32:44,900 --> 00:32:48,270
But if you keep going on without eating, drinking, and resting,

312
00:32:48,270 --> 00:32:50,460
maybe you won't be able to continue living.

313
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:08,850
Drink the porridge.

314
00:33:10,700 --> 00:33:12,960
If you don't drink it,

315
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:16,270
then I will order my men to carry A'Du somewhere else.

316
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:18,730
You won't see her again.

317
00:33:22,610 --> 00:33:24,040
Men!

318
00:33:26,210 --> 00:33:28,180
Carry A'Du out.

319
00:33:28,180 --> 00:33:30,980
Or she might transfer an illness to Crown Princess Consort.

320
00:33:30,980 --> 00:33:32,400
Yes.

321
00:33:59,310 --> 00:34:03,060
I finished drinking it. You can leave now.

322
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:12,440
If I find out again that you have not eaten any of your meals,

323
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:15,110
then I will order them to take A'Du away immediately.

324
00:34:32,170 --> 00:34:35,640
Your Imperial Highness, a secret report from Lord Zhao from the border.

325
00:34:59,190 --> 00:35:02,410
The reason you are here,

326
00:35:02,410 --> 00:35:06,320
- I knew that already.
- Since you knew,

327
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:09,080
then may I ask you.

328
00:35:09,080 --> 00:35:12,600
How did the Bingzhou case go?

329
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:14,280
It went very well.

330
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:18,030
About the evidence of Gao Yuming bribing the candidates' families to shut their mouths,

331
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:20,300
did you obtain it?

332
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:22,020
Yes, I did.

333
00:35:22,020 --> 00:35:25,370
Then may I ask you.

334
00:35:25,370 --> 00:35:28,570
Why didn't you impeach Prime Minister Gao in the imperial court?

335
00:35:28,570 --> 00:35:32,770
Did you get scared at the last moment?

336
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:38,120
When I went to Bingzhou to work on that case, I thought it would be full of obstacles.

337
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:41,250
But who would have thought that everything went so smoothly?

338
00:35:41,250 --> 00:35:47,330
Wherever I went, it's like someone already arranged it and was waiting for me to find out.

339
00:35:48,310 --> 00:35:52,350
All of the spearheads are pointing towards Prime Minister Gao.

340
00:35:52,350 --> 00:35:55,770
I don't know who would make such painstaking effort

341
00:35:55,770 --> 00:35:58,300
to bring forward such a huge bloody storm.

342
00:35:58,300 --> 00:36:03,060
This person's position cannot be lower than Prime Minister Gao's.

343
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:05,410
Hence, you're hesitating?

344
00:36:05,410 --> 00:36:07,910
Because you don't want to become someone's chess piece,

345
00:36:07,910 --> 00:36:12,810
and you're not willing to let other people make the utmost profit from it. Right?

346
00:36:12,810 --> 00:36:14,510
Yes.

347
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:21,980
Lord Zong, do you know what you're doing makes no difference from Gao Yuming,

348
00:36:21,980 --> 00:36:24,670
who only cares about his own personal gain

349
00:36:24,670 --> 00:36:26,210
and disregards the country?

350
00:36:26,210 --> 00:36:29,790
Xi Qingzhuo, please abandon your old-school temperament.

351
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:32,350
Think about the ending of the old grand preceptor!

352
00:36:32,350 --> 00:36:34,000
Forget it!

353
00:36:38,140 --> 00:36:42,950
Lord Zong, at this very moment,

354
00:36:42,950 --> 00:36:45,860
you think you're not helping a tyrant to victimize his subjects.

355
00:36:45,860 --> 00:36:48,910
Then, you can feel at ease as an onlooker?

356
00:36:48,910 --> 00:36:50,240
No...

357
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:52,380
You are wrong!

358
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:58,100
You, I, and every single official

359
00:36:58,100 --> 00:37:02,140
are the mortise and tenon of this imperial court.

360
00:37:02,140 --> 00:37:06,530
It is because we strictly stick by our duty; hence, it is able to be stable.

361
00:37:06,530 --> 00:37:09,920
If we waver, this huge building will then collapse.

362
00:37:09,920 --> 00:37:12,860
No one can keep themselves out of this!

363
00:37:13,610 --> 00:37:16,310
If you read all those books of good conduct and virtue for nothing,

364
00:37:16,310 --> 00:37:21,020
then you can wait and see

365
00:37:21,020 --> 00:37:24,070
how this imperial court will fall apart and collapse.

366
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:29,060
It will bury everyone, including me and you!

367
00:37:29,060 --> 00:37:30,900
All right.

368
00:37:30,900 --> 00:37:33,500
Please say no more, Lord Xi.

369
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:37,950
Your words have made me feel ashamed.

370
00:37:37,950 --> 00:37:39,610
All right!

371
00:37:39,610 --> 00:37:45,570
Since Lord Xi has already put your life and death aside, then I will accompany you!

372
00:37:45,570 --> 00:37:51,790
Even if my life is at stake, I will investigate this case til the very end!

373
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,940
Lord Zong!

374
00:37:58,520 --> 00:38:00,690
Lord Xi!

375
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:09,170
[Courthouse]

376
00:39:22,660 --> 00:39:25,170
Father, it turns out that the one who led the mass suicide of the examiners

377
00:39:25,170 --> 00:39:26,700
then was an old xiucai.
(T/N: "xiucai" is the term given for examiners who have passed initial local exams and qualified to take the imperial civil exam)

378
00:39:26,700 --> 00:39:29,880
His hometown is Bingzhou, from the administrative division named Zong Huan.

379
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:33,700
Thirty years ago, Zong Huan's initial studies started with this person,

380
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:37,010
