381
00:39:37,920 --> 00:39:43,930
It looks like the slight worrying I have been experiencing these days didn't come up for no reason.

382
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:47,230
Zong Huan.

383
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:53,580
What is going on in the palace?

384
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:57,510
I heard His Imperial Majesty was furious.

385
00:39:57,510 --> 00:40:01,360
Did he see anyone today?

386
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:04,400
He didn't ask for Zong Huan, who wrote the memorial.

387
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:08,100
Neither did he see Xi Qingzhou. He just asked for the crown prince.

388
00:40:26,450 --> 00:40:28,580
My Lady Noble Consort.

389
00:40:28,580 --> 00:40:32,300
Greetings to Your Imperial Majesty.

390
00:40:38,900 --> 00:40:45,010
